      <div class="content"> <div class="entity entity-bean bean-stanford-postcard clearfix" about="/block/accessibility-information" typeof="">

  <div class="content">
    <div id="bean-stanford-postcard-full-group-s-postcard--3" class="postcard group-s-postcard field-group-div"><div id="bean-stanford-postcard-full-group-s-postcard-content--3" class="postcard-content group-s-postcard-content field-group-div"><div class="field field-name-field-s-postcard-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>If you have trouble accessing content or using features of this website due to a disability, please contact us via <a href="http://helpsu.stanford.edu/?pcat=webaccessibility">HelpSU</a>. </p>
<p>You can also email us at <a href="mailto:web-accessibility@stanford.edu" rel="nofollow">web-accessibility@stanford.edu</a>. </p>
